quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,23,"Likewise, We sentno warner before you<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>to any town but its affluent ones said, “Indeed, we found our forefathers on a course<a class=""sup""><sup>b </sup></a>, and indeed we are following in their footsteps.”"
  43,24,"<span class=""h"">He would say<sup foot_note=""81104"" class=""qiraat"">1</sup> </span>, “Even if <span class=""h"">I<sup foot_note=""81105"" class=""qiraat"">2</sup> </span><span class=""h"">have come to you</span><a class=""sup""><sup>pl </sup></a>with better guidance than what you found your forefathers following?” They would say, “Indeed, we deny what you<a class=""sup""><sup>pl </sup></a>are sent with.”"
  43,25,"Thus We took retribution on them, so look<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>at what the outcome was for the disbelievers."
  43,26,"And recall when Abraham said to his father and his people, “I am innocent of what you worship"
  43,27,"except for the One Who originated me, for He will guide me.”"
  43,28,"And he made it an enduring word in his posterity, so that they may return."
  43,29,"Yet I let these and their forefathers enjoy<i class=""s"">(life) </i>until the truth and an evident messenger came to them."
  43,30,"But when the truth came to them, they said, “This is sorcery, and indeed we are deniers of it.”"
  43,31,"They also said, “If only this Recital{1}had been sent down to any great man from the two towns{2}.”",footnotes:1:The Arabic word used is Qur’anwhich literally means ‘recital’ or ‘recitation’.|2:Makkah and Al-ta’if.
  43,32,"Is it they who allocate the mercy of your<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>Lord? It is We who have allocated their livelihood in the Earlier Life. And We elevated some of them by degrees above others, that some of them may employ one another in service. But your Lord’s mercy is better than what they hoard."
  43,33,"Were it not that humanity would become a single<i class=""s"">(ungodly) </i>community, We would have provided those who deny the All-Merciful with <span class=""h"">roofs<sup foot_note=""81108"" class=""qiraat"">1</sup> </span>of silver to their houses, and stairways<i class=""s"">(of silver) </i>by which they ascend,"
